<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276537>
    dc:description "FIGURES 93 – 97. Aulopocella americana n. sp., off São Paulo, Brazil (REVIZEE station 6693). 93, Small colony growing on Conescharellidae; 94, another colony found on Conescharellidae, 95, close-up of colony showing ovicelled zooids and autozooid with tubular peristome (bellow); 96, close-up of orifice and large interzooidal avicularia; 97, large colony with secondary calcification." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/276537/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

